<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logo-small.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.10/css/all.css"
        integrity="sha384-+d0P83n9kaQMCwj8F4RJB66tzIwOKmrdb46+porD/OvrJ+37WqIM7UoBtwHO6Nlg" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/jquery/latest/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css" />
    <title>Избори България - Партии</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{>login}}
    {{>header}}

    <div id="carousel-titles">
        <h1>Партии</h1>
        <p>Разгледайте регистрираните партии за предстоящите избори и вземете своето решение!</p>
    </div>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="4"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="5"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/sancho.jpg" alt="First slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #fff;">Лека нощ</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Сънчо</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> Време е за сън!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/vader.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #cc6666;">Нова империя</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Дарт Вейдър</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> За тъмната страна!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/snejanka.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #339900;">Близката гора</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Снежанка</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> Красотата ще спаси света!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/uncle-s.jpg" alt="Fourth slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #ffcc33;">Златните патоци</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Чичо Скрудж</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> Който пести, има пари!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/night-king.jpg" alt="Fifth slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #006699;">Скръц-скръц</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Нощният крал</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> Зимата иде!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="/img/timon-pumba.jpg" alt="Sixth slide">
                <div class="party-titles">
                    <h2 style="color: #ff6633;">Коалиция за <br>червейчета</h2>
                    <h3><em>Водач:</em> Тимон и Пумба</h3>
                    <p><em>Лозунг:</em> Хакуна матата!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="after-carousel">
        <h3>Вижте основните точки в програмата на всяка партия.</h3>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Партия</th>
                    <th>Програма</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Лека нощ</td>
                    <td>По 2 часа повече сън на ден.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Нова империя</td>
                    <td>Наказваме неподчинението.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Близката гора</td>
                    <td>Не на черните магии и измамниците.
                        <br>Безплатни ябълки всяка седмица.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Златните патоци</td>
                    <td>Ние не харчим излишни пари.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Скръц-скръц</td>
                    <td>Пренаписване на последните 3 сезона на GoT.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Коалиция за червейчета</td>
                    <td>Безплатна порция буболечки всеки месец.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    {{>footer}}
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/bundle.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>